From: DevBox UML arm64 Port
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: um: add asm/segment.h stub

arm64 has no GDT/TLS segments (x86-specific concept).
Stub required because arch/um/include/asm/thread_info.h includes it unconditionally.

--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm64/um/asm/segment.h
@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0 */
+/* arm64 has no GDT/TLS segments — stub for UML build compatibility */
+#ifndef __UM_SEGMENT_ARM64_H
+#define __UM_SEGMENT_ARM64_H
+
+/* arm64 does not use GDT entries or TLS segments like x86 */
+
+#endif
